CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Acumen Pharmaceuticals Inc is a clinical-stage biopharmaceutical company developing a novel disease-modifying approach to target what we believe to be a key underlying cause of Alzheimer's disease. The company's lead drug candidate, ACU193, is a subclass monoclonal antibody which selectively targets amyloid-beta oligomers.
